name: Sawblade Scamp
oracle_text:
Haste
Whenever you cast a noncreature spell, put an oil counter on Sawblade Scamp.
{T}, Remove an oil counter from Sawblade Scamp: It deals 1 damage to each opponent.
flavor_text: Be the blade that severs hierarchy.

name: Urabrask's Anointer
oracle_text: When Urabrask's Anointer enters the battlefield, it deals X damage to any target, where X is the number of permanents you control with oil counters on them.
flavor_text: Will you be the flame which burns the world, or merely be consumed as fuel?

name: The Filigree Sylex
oracle_text:
{T}: Put an oil counter on The Filigree Sylex.
{T}, Sacrifice The Filigree Sylex: Destroy each nonland permanent with mana value equal to the number of oil counters on The Filigree Sylex.
{T}, Remove ten oil counters from among permanents you control and sacrifice The Filigree Sylex: It deals 10 damage to any target.

name: Vraan, Executioner Thane
oracle_text: Whenever one or more other creatures you control die, each opponent loses 2 life and you gain 2 life. This ability triggers only once each turn.
flavor_text: "Soon enough each praetor will have hired me to kill the others, and I will stand alone as the true Father of Machines."

name: Transplant Theorist
oracle_text:
Whenever Transplant Theorist or another artifact enters the battlefield under your control, you may draw a card. If you do, discard a card.
{2}: Put target card from your graveyard on the bottom of your library.

name: Magmatic Sprinter
oracle_text:
Haste
When Magmatic Sprinter enters the battlefield, put two oil counters on target artifact or creature you control.
At the beginning of your ned step, return Magmatic Sprinter to its owner's hand unless you remove two oil counters from it.

name: Cankerbloom
oracle_text:
{1}, Sacrifice Cankerbloom: Choose one —
• Destroy target artifact.
• Destroy target enchantment.
• Proliferate.

name: Phyrexian Vindicator
oracle_text:
Flying
If damage would be dealt to Phyrexian Vindicator, prevent that damage. When damage is prevented this way, Phyrexian Vindicator deals that much damage to any other target.

name: Bladed Ambassador
oracle_text:
Bladed Ambassador enters the battlefield with an oil counter on it.
{1}, Remove an oil counter from Bladed Ambassador: Bladed Ambassador gains indestructible until end of turn.
flavor_text: "Let those thanebound dissenters prattle about their dead god. I serve the Mother of Machines, and in her name I carve out their heresy."

name: Tamiyo's Logbook
oracle_text: {5}{U}, {T}: Draw a card. This ability costs {1} less to activate for each other artifact you control.
flavor_text:
"We are opening a new chapter in the one true story of Phyrexia. Someone must record it for posterity."
—Tamiyo

name: Serum Snare
oracle_text: Return target nonland permanent to its owner's hand. If that permanent had mana value 3 or less, proliferate. (Choose any number of permanents and/or players, then give each another counter of each kind already there.)
flavor_text: "I bring a message from the Autonomous Fern—argh!"

name: Furnace Punisher
oracle_text:
Menace
At the beginning of each player's upkeep, Furnace Punisher deals 2 damage to that player unless they control two or more basic lands.
flavor_text: She marks her favorite creations with a searing brand, leaving all others to be consumed by the furnace.

name: Atraxa's Skitterfang
oracle_text:
Atraxa's Skitterfang enters the battlefield with three oil counters on it.
At the beginning of combat on your turn, you may remove an oil counter from Atraxa's Skitterfang. When you do, target creature you control gains your choice of flying, vigilance, deathtouch, or lifelink until end of turn.

name: Ambulatory Edifice
oracle_text: When Ambulatory Edifice enters the battlefield, you may pay 2 life. When you do, target creature gets -1/-1 until end of turn.
flavor_text: The Mirran forces thought they'd vanquished their foes . . . until a nearby monument go up and started stalking towards them.

name: Watchful Blisterzoa
oracle_text:
Flying
 Watchful Blisterzoa enters the battlefield with an oil counter on it.
When Watchful Blisterzoa dies, draw a cards equal to the number of oil counters on it.
flavor_text: After a series of ambushes, Uulbrek demanded a sentry with no blind spots.
